results.name: Permutation of natural numbers: a(n) = A246264(A064216(2*n)).
comment: This permutation is induced when A064216 is restricted to even numbers (equally, when A064989 is restricted to the numbers of form 4n-1) and the resulting numbers are "ranked" with A246264.
